{
  "uid": "tempo-dex-monitoring",
  "title": "StablecoinDEX Monitoring",
  "description": "Real-time orderbook health: spread, liquidity, slippage, and activity for all StablecoinDEX trading pairs.",
  "tags": ["tempo", "dex"],
  "editable": true,
  "schemaVersion": 39,
  "graphTooltip": 1,
  "time": {
    "from": "now-5m",
    "to": "now"
  },
  "refresh": "5s",
  "fiscalYearStartMonth": 0,
  "id": null,
  "links": [],
  "templating": {
    "list": [
      {
        "name": "chain_id",
        "label": "Chain",
        "type": "query",
        "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "Prometheus" },
        "query": "label_values(tempo_dex_total_orders, chain_id)",
        "refresh": 2,
        "includeAll": false,
        "current": {},
        "sort": 1
      },
      {
        "name": "base_name",
        "label": "Pair",
        "type": "query",
        "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "Prometheus" },
        "query": "label_values({__name__=~\"tempo_dex_best.*\", chain_id=\"$chain_id\"}, base_name)",
        "refresh": 2,
        "includeAll": true,
        "multi": true,
        "current": {},
        "sort": 1
      }
    ]
  },
  "panels": [
    {
      "title": "",
      "type": "text",
      "gridPos": { "h": 3, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 0 },
      "id": 10,
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "### StablecoinDEX Health Monitor\nReal-time orderbook metrics from Tempo's on-chain DEX. **Spread** = price gap between buyers and sellers. **Liquidity** = volume available at best price. **Slippage** = price impact of a $1000 swap.\n\nBackground zones: \ud83d\udfe2 **Green** = healthy &nbsp; \ud83d\udfe1 **Yellow** = moderate risk &nbsp; \ud83d\udd34 **Red** = needs attention. Spread: <10 / 10-30 / >30 ticks. Slippage: <50 / 50-150 / >150 bps."
      }
    },
    {
      "title": "Spread — Price Efficiency",
      "description": "Difference between best ask and best bid in ticks. Lower = tighter market. Green (<10) = healthy, Yellow (10-30) = moderate, Red (>30) = wide.",
      "type": "timeseries",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "Prometheus"
      },
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 16, "x": 0, "y": 3 },
      "id": 1,
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": { "mode": "palette-classic" },
          "custom": {
            "drawStyle": "line",
            "lineInterpolation": "smooth",
            "lineWidth": 2,
            "fillOpacity": 10,
            "gradientMode": "none",
            "showPoints": "never",
            "spanNulls": false,
            "axisBorderShow": false,
            "axisCenteredZero": false,
            "axisColorMode": "text",
            "axisLabel": "",
            "axisPlacement": "auto",
            "scaleDistribution": { "type": "linear" },
            "stacking": { "group": "A", "mode": "none" },
            "thresholdsStyle": { "mode": "line+area" }
          },
          "unit": "none",
          "min": 0,
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              { "color": "transparent", "value": null },
              { "color": "rgba(50, 172, 45, 0.1)", "value": 0 },
              { "color": "rgba(237, 129, 40, 0.15)", "value": 10 },
              { "color": "rgba(245, 54, 54, 0.15)", "value": 30 }
            ]
          }
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "options": {
        "legend": {
          "displayMode": "list",
          "placement": "bottom",
          "showLegend": false
        },
        "tooltip": { "mode": "multi", "sort": "desc" }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "Prometheus" },
          "expr": "tempo_dex_spread_ticks{chain_id=\"$chain_id\", base_name=~\"$base_name\"}",
          "legendFormat": "{{base_name}}",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "title": "Total Orders",
      "description": "Total number of orders ever created across all pairs. Indicates overall DEX activity.",
      "type": "stat",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "Prometheus"
      },
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 4, "x": 16, "y": 3 },
      "id": 2,
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": { "mode": "thresholds" },
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              { "color": "blue", "value": null }
            ]
          },
          "unit": "short",
          "mappings": []
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "options": {
        "reduceOptions": {
          "values": false,
          "calcs": ["lastNotNull"],
          "fields": ""
        },
        "orientation": "auto",
        "textMode": "auto",
        "colorMode": "value",
        "graphMode": "area",
        "justifyMode": "auto"
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "Prometheus" },
          "expr": "tempo_dex_total_orders{chain_id=\"$chain_id\"}",
          "legendFormat": "Orders",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "title": "Monitor Errors",
      "description": "RPC errors encountered while fetching DEX data. Grouped by call type: next_order_id, books, tick_level_bid, tick_level_ask.",
      "type": "stat",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "Prometheus"
      },
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 4, "x": 20, "y": 3 },
      "id": 6,
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": { "mode": "thresholds" },
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              { "color": "green", "value": null },
              { "color": "yellow", "value": 1 },
              { "color": "red", "value": 10 }
            ]
          },
          "unit": "short",
          "mappings": []
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "options": {
        "reduceOptions": {
          "values": false,
          "calcs": ["lastNotNull"],
          "fields": ""
        },
        "orientation": "auto",
        "textMode": "auto",
        "colorMode": "value",
        "graphMode": "area",
        "justifyMode": "auto"
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "Prometheus" },
          "expr": "increase(tempo_dex_monitor_errors{chain_id=\"$chain_id\"}[5m])",
          "legendFormat": "{{request}}",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "title": "Bid Depth — Buy Side",
      "description": "Total liquidity at the best bid (buy) price. Higher = more buyers ready to trade. Drop to 0 means no buy orders.",
      "type": "timeseries",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "Prometheus"
      },
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 0, "y": 11 },
      "id": 3,
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": { "mode": "palette-classic" },
          "custom": {
            "drawStyle": "line",
            "lineInterpolation": "smooth",
            "lineWidth": 1,
            "fillOpacity": 20,
            "gradientMode": "opacity",
            "showPoints": "never",
            "spanNulls": false,
            "axisBorderShow": false,
            "axisCenteredZero": false,
            "axisColorMode": "text",
            "axisLabel": "",
            "axisPlacement": "auto",
            "scaleDistribution": { "type": "linear" },
            "stacking": { "group": "A", "mode": "none" },
            "thresholdsStyle": { "mode": "off" }
          },
          "unit": "short",
          "min": 0
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "options": {
        "legend": {
          "displayMode": "list",
          "placement": "bottom",
          "showLegend": false
        },
        "tooltip": { "mode": "multi", "sort": "desc" }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "Prometheus" },
          "expr": "tempo_dex_best_bid_liquidity{chain_id=\"$chain_id\", base_name=~\"$base_name\"}",
          "legendFormat": "{{base_name}}",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "title": "Ask Depth — Sell Side",
      "description": "Total liquidity at the best ask (sell) price. Higher = more sellers ready to trade. Drop to 0 means no sell orders.",
      "type": "timeseries",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "Prometheus"
      },
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 12, "y": 11 },
      "id": 4,
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": { "mode": "palette-classic" },
          "custom": {
            "drawStyle": "line",
            "lineInterpolation": "smooth",
            "lineWidth": 1,
            "fillOpacity": 20,
            "gradientMode": "opacity",
            "showPoints": "never",
            "spanNulls": false,
            "axisBorderShow": false,
            "axisCenteredZero": false,
            "axisColorMode": "text",
            "axisLabel": "",
            "axisPlacement": "auto",
            "scaleDistribution": { "type": "linear" },
            "stacking": { "group": "A", "mode": "none" },
            "thresholdsStyle": { "mode": "off" }
          },
          "unit": "short",
          "min": 0
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "options": {
        "legend": {
          "displayMode": "list",
          "placement": "bottom",
          "showLegend": false
        },
        "tooltip": { "mode": "multi", "sort": "desc" }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "Prometheus" },
          "expr": "tempo_dex_best_ask_liquidity{chain_id=\"$chain_id\", base_name=~\"$base_name\"}",
          "legendFormat": "{{base_name}}",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "title": "Slippage — Swap Cost Estimation",
      "description": "Estimated price impact for a $1000 swap. Green (<50 bps) = low cost, Yellow (50-150 bps) = moderate, Red (>150 bps) = expensive. 1 bps = 0.01%.",
      "type": "timeseries",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "Prometheus"
      },
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 19 },
      "id": 5,
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": { "mode": "palette-classic" },
          "custom": {
            "drawStyle": "line",
            "lineInterpolation": "smooth",
            "lineWidth": 2,
            "fillOpacity": 10,
            "gradientMode": "none",
            "showPoints": "never",
            "spanNulls": false,
            "axisBorderShow": false,
            "axisCenteredZero": false,
            "axisColorMode": "text",
            "axisLabel": "",
            "axisPlacement": "auto",
            "scaleDistribution": { "type": "linear" },
            "stacking": { "group": "A", "mode": "none" },
            "thresholdsStyle": {
              "mode": "line+area"
            }
          },
          "unit": "none",
          "min": 0,
          "noValue": "No liquidity data",
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              { "color": "transparent", "value": null },
              { "color": "rgba(50, 172, 45, 0.1)", "value": 0 },
              { "color": "rgba(237, 129, 40, 0.15)", "value": 50 },
              { "color": "rgba(245, 54, 54, 0.15)", "value": 150 }
            ]
          }
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "options": {
        "legend": {
          "displayMode": "list",
          "placement": "bottom",
          "showLegend": false
        },
        "tooltip": { "mode": "multi", "sort": "desc" }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "Prometheus" },
          "expr": "tempo_dex_slippage_bps{chain_id=\"$chain_id\", base_name=~\"$base_name\"}",
          "legendFormat": "{{base_name}}",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
  "annotations": { "list": [] }
}
